Package: VectorCodeR
Type: Package
Title: VectorCodeR
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("PWH", "Kwong", email = "wai-hang.kwong@polyu.edu.hk", role = "aut"),
    person("Zhexuan", "GU", email = "22054513g@connect.polyu.hk", role = "cre"))
Maintainer: Zhexuan GU <22054513g@connect.polyu.hk>
Description: VectorCodeR is an R package designed to facilitate the analysis of inter-limb and intra-limb coordination in human movement. It provides functions for calculating the phase angle between two segments, enabling researchers and practitioners to quantify the coordination patterns within and between limbs during various motor tasks.
License: GPL-3
